{"tid":1827702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【客死異鄉】一男一女中國遊客 冰島「飛機殘骸」景點附近死亡","createTime":"2020-01-17T07:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T18:14:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc7403ef4ae9cc754516dcc713390f0d97d1509","tid":1827702,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:00:19.000Z","msg":"一男一女中國公民周四被發現倒斃冰島南部景點「飛機殘骸」（Solheimasandur Plane Wreck）附近，死因尚待查明。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐冰島大使館接獲冰島警方通知後，迅速啟動領保應急機制，向冰島警方進一步了解情況，要求警方儘快查明死因。<br />\n<br />\n冰島近日連續出現暴風雪惡劣天氣及雪崩等自然災害，對遊客出行安全造成嚴重影響。中國駐冰島大使館提醒訪冰中國遊客，務必密切關注當地天氣及道路狀況，遵守安全提示及道路交通規則，注意行車和人身安全。<br />\n<br />\nSolheimasandur黑沙灘位於冰島南方，當地最著名的景點是美軍DC-3飛機殘骸。1973年11月24日一架美軍DC-3飛機因天氣惡劣急降冰島，結果意外墜落該處，機上所有人生還，但飛機嚴重損毀，美軍鑑於回收飛機殘骸成本過高，決定任由飛機殘骸遺留該處，自此成為著名景點。<br />\n<br />\n一名香港男子與一班友人2016年到Solheimasandur黑沙灘自駕遊期間遇車禍喪生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200117/large/1579219115_be66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200117%2Flarge%2F1579219115_be66.jpg&h=c9d27537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名中國遊客被發現死於冰島「飛機殘骸」景點附近。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200117/KMFMBS5YDVP6XQ7TU3ALTZUPIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200117%2FKMFMBS5YDVP6XQ7TU3ALTZUPIQ%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcylm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=c8d5bc87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200117%2FKMFMBS5YDVP6XQ7TU3ALTZUPIQ%2F&h=86d02b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200117/KMFMBS5YDVP6XQ7TU3ALTZUPIQ/</a>"},{"pid":"1e6c7e06a13aab4151d7121b3fdaa87d40ab1c89","tid":1827702,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"dea2c2071cd9c272e4ef42130782df4f61424601","tid":1827702,"uid":275613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,